New workflow scripts in `scripts/`:
- `context-workflow.sh`: recommended arrival workflow (current file note, parent dirs/root, current commit, imports, optional history)
- `path-history.sh`: historical file notes via git log + rev-parse
- `note-history.sh`: overwrite history via notes-ref history

These are intentionally repo-level golden workflows rather than new core mycelium commands.
